---
title: Antipasto-Topped Chicken with Balsamic Green Beans and Lemon Orzo
description: Olives, roasted red peppers and mozza combine for an antipasto chicken stuffer! A side of roasted balsamic beans and lemon orzo fill out this appetizer-inspired dinner!
